{"tid":2113822,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"八鄉地產代理爭執擸架生 一男遭圍毆爆頭倒地送院","createTime":"2020-07-18T11:07:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-18T12:24:59.000Z","uid":99493,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"32a6c22bec3594908127cf641c3a4e0cd3728645","tid":2113822,"uid":99493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T11:07:45.000Z","msg":"下午4時許，兩批地產代理，於八鄉高埔徑3號私人屋苑「山水盈」地盤外爭執，原因不明。其間，其中一方兩人突然被4至5人圍毆。警方接報到場時，打人一方已不知所終，事件中有人頭部受創，送博愛醫院治理，亦有人指手提電話被搶走，暫時未有人被捕。<br />\n<br />\n網上流傳片段可見，兩批地產代理一輪推撞後開始毆鬥，其中一名男子被3至4名壯漢圍毆，他不僅衣衫被扯爛，其後更遭推跌倒卧地上，毫無還擊之力。即使如此，壯漢不放過這名男子，繼續追擊拳打腳踢。片段最後，他一名同伴趕至，高舉一張玻璃枱然後怒砸向附近路面，玻璃粉碎散落一地，壯漢見狀始作罷。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20200718/5BF6V25Z6XG4QZRE6E5234F2JI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200718%2F5BF6V25Z6XG4QZRE6E5234F2JI%2F&d=G%2B3HFD3c3HuaSfC8k9KTiRvkGFRp1GVnGvdlwu1qkBE%3D&h=64a8bfe5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200718%2F5BF6V25Z6XG4QZRE6E5234F2JI%2F&h=0e1b26a1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20200718/5BF6V25Z6XG4QZRE6E5234F2JI/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/j4hcoLzo1BM2tijfUZwEfcd_QE0=/480x848/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/LCILF2DZAJXHPQI3A3WKM5HEAM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fj4hcoLzo1BM2tijfUZwEfcd_QE0%3D%2F480x848%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FLCILF2DZAJXHPQI3A3WKM5HEAM.jpg&h=ff2de27e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6c9e2e498f9efc94a1538d743a860d79ad380b91","tid":2113822,"uid":76609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T11:08:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b45c31f7424c4